subject: Figure Skating
Olympic Games
Ice Skating
lead_paragraph: Kimmie Meissner will take the ice as the top American woman at the U.S. Figure Skating Championships Wednesday, a year after winning a surprise world title at age 16 following a sixth-place finish in the Olympics.
